Travel easily with multiple bags. The Never-Lost Attach-A-Bag Strap secures an additional bag to the front of the upright and holds up to 30 lbs (13.6 kg). Lighter. Easier. Better Than Ever. The most popular collection of Victorinox Travel Gear, Werks Traveler™ 4.0 is now better than ever with dual-caster uprights to accommodate the needs of today's traveler. From the makers of the original Swiss Army Knife.
